    {
      "id": "32bb3f8d-de9b-4728-b70a-b048e6a574f7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors present a semi-supervised approach to perform knowledge distillation from multi-modal Big Data. This novel approach exhibits good results for multiple tasks such as emotion recognition or polarity detection → all things that may be useful for an educational context.",
      "raw": {
